    {
      "type": "createWindow",
      "params": {
        "title": "📁 Workspace Templates Manager",
        "content": "<div style=\"padding: 25px; font-family: 'MS Sans Serif'; background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%); height: 100%; overflow-y: auto;\"><h1 style=\"margin: 0 0 20px 0; color: #2c3e50; text-align: center;\">📁 Workspace Templates</h1><p style=\"text-align: center; color: #7f8c8d; margin-bottom: 30px;\">Save and restore your perfect workspace configurations</p><div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 15px; margin: 20px 0;\"><div style=\"background: white; border: 2px solid #3498db; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); cursor: pointer; transition: transform 0.2s;\" onclick=\"executeInstruction('focus-mode')\"><h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #3498db;\">🎯 Deep Work</h3><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; color: #7f8c8d; font-size: 13px;\">Minimalist setup with Notepad and focus timer. Eliminates distractions.</p><div style=\"margin-top: 15px; padding-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #ecf0f1;\"><strong style=\"color: #2c3e50; font-size: 12px;\">Includes:</strong><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0; padding-left: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #7f8c8d;\"><li>Clear desktop</li><li>Notepad (centered)</li><li>Pomodoro timer</li><li>Minimal theme</li></ul></div><div style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 15px;\"><button onclick=\"executeInstruction('focus-mode')\" style=\"background: #3498db; color: white; border: none; padding: 8px 20px; border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold;\">Load Template</button></div></div><div style=\"background: white; border: 2px solid #e74c3c; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); cursor: pointer; transition: transform 0.2s;\" onclick=\"executeInstruction('presentation-mode')\"><h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #e74c3c;\">🎬 Presentation</h3><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; color: #7f8c8d; font-size: 13px;\">Professional demo setup with organized layout and key information windows.</p><div style=\"margin-top: 15px; padding-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #ecf0f1;\"><strong style=\"color: #2c3e50; font-size: 12px;\">Includes:</strong><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0; padding-left: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #7f8c8d;\"><li>Overview window</li><li>Key innovations</li><li>Live demo controls</li><li>Cascaded layout</li></ul></div><div style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 15px;\"><button onclick=\"executeInstruction('presentation-mode')\" style=\"background: #e74c3c; color: white; border: none; padding: 8px 20px; border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold;\">Load Template</button></div></div><div style=\"background: white; border: 2px solid #2ecc71; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\"><h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #2ecc71;\">📚 Learning</h3><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; color: #7f8c8d; font-size: 13px;\">Interactive tutorial environment with step-by-step guides and practice console.</p><div style=\"margin-top: 15px; padding-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #ecf0f1;\"><strong style=\"color: #2c3e50; font-size: 12px;\">Includes:</strong><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0; padding-left: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #7f8c8d;\"><li>Tutorial windows</li><li>Practice console</li><li>Quick reference</li><li>Progress tracking</li></ul></div><div style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 15px;\"><button onclick=\"executeInstruction('learning-assistant-tutorial')\" style=\"background: #2ecc71; color: white; border: none; padding: 8px 20px; border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold;\">Load Template</button></div></div><div style=\"background: white; border: 2px solid #f39c12; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\"><h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #f39c12;\">🧹 Clean Slate</h3><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; color: #7f8c8d; font-size: 13px;\">Organize and tidy up your workspace. Perfect for starting fresh.</p><div style=\"margin-top: 15px; padding-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #ecf0f1;\"><strong style=\"color: #2c3e50; font-size: 12px;\">Includes:</strong><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0; padding-left: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #7f8c8d;\"><li>Icon organization</li><li>Window cascade</li><li>Taskbar cleanup</li><li>Fresh start</li></ul></div><div style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 15px;\"><button onclick=\"executeInstruction('cleanup-workspace')\" style=\"background: #f39c12; color: white; border: none; padding: 8px 20px; border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold;\">Load Template</button></div></div></div><div style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 30px 0; color: white;\"><h2 style=\"margin: 0 0 15px 0;\">💡 Smart Suggestions</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0; line-height: 1.6;\">The system learns your patterns and suggests templates at the right time:</p><ul style=\"margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px; line-height: 1.8;\"><li>🌅 <strong>Morning (9 AM):</strong> Suggests your morning routine</li><li>🎯 <strong>Many windows open:</strong> Suggests cleanup</li><li>⏰ <strong>End of day:</strong> Prompts to save state</li><li>🔄 <strong>Repetitive patterns:</strong> Auto-generates new templates</li></ul></div><div style=\"background: white; border: 2px solid #95a5a6; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0;\"><h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 15px 0; color: #2c3e50;\">🔧 Advanced: Create Custom Template</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0; color: #7f8c8d; line-height: 1.6;\">You can create your own workspace templates as JSON instruction files. Here's how:</p><div style=\"background: #2c3e50; color: #ecf0f1; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 15px 0; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 12px; overflow-x: auto;\"><pre style=\"margin: 0;\">// 1. Set up your ideal workspace manually\\n// 2. Export the state:\\nconst myWorkspace = getLatestState()\\n\\n// 3. Create instruction file that recreates it:\\nconst template = {\\n  \"name\": \"my-custom-workspace\",\\n  \"description\": \"My perfect setup\",\\n  \"steps\": [/* your steps */]\\n}\\n\\n// 4. Save to .ai/static-instructions/</pre></div><p style=\"margin: 10px 0; color: #7f8c8d; font-size: 13px; font-style: italic;\">Pro tip: Study existing instruction files to learn the patterns!</p></div></div>",
        "width": 750,
        "height": 600,
        "x": 40,
        "y": 20
      },
      "description": "Create workspace templates manager window",
      "delay": 500
    },
    {
      "type": "createWindow",
      "params": {
        "title": "📊 Activity Analytics",
        "content": "<div style=\"padding: 20px; font-family: 'MS Sans Serif'; background: #1e1e1e; color: #d4d4d4; height: 100%;\"><h2 style=\"margin: 0 0 20px 0; color: #4ec9b0; border-bottom: 2px solid #4ec9b0; padding-bottom: 10px;\">📊 Workspace Usage Patterns</h2><div style=\"background: #252526; border: 1px solid #3e3e42; border-radius: 4px; padding: 20px; margin: 15px 0;\"><h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 15px 0; color: #569cd6;\">📈 Today's Activity</h3><div style=\"margin: 15px 0;\"><div style=\"margin: 10px 0;\"><div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 5px;\"><span style=\"color: #ce9178;\">Windows Created:</span><span style=\"color: #b5cea8; font-weight: bold;\">23</span></div><div style=\"background: #3e3e42; height: 8px; border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden;\"><div style=\"background: #4ec9b0; height: 100%; width: 76%;\"></div></div></div><div style=\"margin: 10px 0;\"><div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 5px;\"><span style=\"color: #ce9178;\">Templates Used:</span><span style=\"color: #b5cea8; font-weight: bold;\">7</span></div><div style=\"background: #3e3e42; height: 8px; border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden;\"><div style=\"background: #569cd6; height: 100%; width: 47%;\"></div></div></div><div style=\"margin: 10px 0;\"><div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 5px;\"><span style=\"color: #ce9178;\">State Saves:</span><span style=\"color: #b5cea8; font-weight: bold;\">15</span></div><div style=\"background: #3e3e42; height: 8px; border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden;\"><div style=\"background: #c586c0; height: 100%; width: 60%;\"></div></div></div></div></div><div style=\"background: #0e639c; border-left: 4px solid #007acc; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 4px;\"><h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #fff;\">💡 Insight</h3><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; line-height: 1.6;\">You use Focus Mode most frequently between 9-11 AM. Consider making this your default morning template!</p></div><div style=\"background: #252526; border: 1px solid #3e3e42; border-radius: 4px; padding: 20px; margin: 15px 0;\"><h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 15px 0; color: #569cd6;\">🎯 Popular Templates</h3><ol style=\"margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; line-height: 2;\"><li style=\"color: #4ec9b0;\">Focus Mode <span style=\"color: #7f8c8d;\">(42% of sessions)</span></li><li style=\"color: #4ec9b0;\">Cleanup Workspace <span style=\"color: #7f8c8d;\">(28% of sessions)</span></li><li style=\"color: #4ec9b0;\">Presentation Mode <span style=\"color: #7f8c8d;\">(18% of sessions)</span></li><li style=\"color: #4ec9b0;\">Learning Mode <span style=\"color: #7f8c8d;\">(12% of sessions)</span></li></ol></div><div style=\"background: #1a1a1a; border: 1px solid #3e3e42; border-radius: 4px; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; text-align: center;\"><p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #9cdcfe;\">🔮 AI Suggestion</p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0; color: #d4d4d4; line-height: 1.6;\">Based on your patterns, would you like to create a \"Morning Coding\" template that combines Focus Mode with specific development tools?</p><button style=\"background: #0e639c; color: white; border: none; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 4px; margin-top: 10px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold;\">✨ Generate Template</button></div></div>",
        "width": 450,
        "height": 600,
        "x": 320,
        "y": 50
      },
      "description": "Create analytics dashboard",
      "delay": 500
    },
    {
      "type": "cascadeWindows",
      "params": {
        "startX": 60,
        "startY": 30,
        "offsetX": 40,
        "offsetY": 40
      },
      "description": "Arrange workspace manager windows",
      "delay": 600
    },
    {
      "type": "playSound",
      "params": {
        "sound": "notify"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "notification",
      "params": {
        "title": "✅ Workspace Manager Ready",
        "message": "Browse templates, view analytics, and manage your perfect workspaces!"
      }
